"    Extrahepatic primary sclerosing cholangitis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 296px; height: 252px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Ultrasound image of the right upper quadrant in a patient with ulcerative colitis and primary sclerosing cholangitis shows marked thickening of the wall of the common bile duct (large arrows) and narrowing of its lumen (small arrows).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
